data.description: Located on a quiet cul-de-sac on the Manhattan East side, this 4 bedroom, 4 bathroom has a newly finished basement, fresh paint inside, and engineered hardwood floors.  This unique layout has large bedrooms, plenty of closet space and storage.  There is a bathroom for every bedroom which is always a nice feature.  The Primary En Suite is a great space with double sinks, a nice shower and great closet spaces.  The garage space is great for workout equipment a small shop and so much more.  Come take a look today!
